channel.title: Webclient
channel.description:
Alright well I got my webclient to load, I logged in and everything until I remembered i didn't change some interfaces to the new cache location, so I change them and rejar and resign and everything, but now when it loads once it says "Connecting to file server" it skips everything else it just displays the login page, and when I try to login it stays at "Connecting to server" so I'm guessing that because it doesn't load everything it's not logging in right?
It's been awhile since I've worked with webclients but if someone could help I'd appreciate it, if you need to see for yourself just let me know.
Here's a picture: [img]http://i36.tinypic.com/1hozsk.png[/img]
I think it's something cache related but not 100% sure, any tips would be helpful.
